      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>This gritty orange fluid has a tart taste. When you drink this potion, select a single language you know fluently. You must select a language that you know permanently; this doesn’t function with a language you’ve learned temporarily, such as through a class ability or spell. For 1 hour after drinking this serum, you also know the following that you don’t already know: the signed, spoken, and tactile versions of the selected language. While this serum grants comprehension and knowledge of these versions of the language, it doesn’t alter any of your senses.</p>"
